            <title><![CDATA[【[衰]#突发突止的牙痛警惕三叉神经痛#】#有一种牙痛源自三叉神经痛# 专家提醒，牙痛未必是牙病，可能神经在找茬！专家介绍，三叉神经分为三支，其中第三支为下...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[衰]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuai-285d2d97c7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%AA%81%E5%8F%91%E7%AA%81%E6%AD%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%89%99%E7%97%9B%E8%AD%A6%E6%83%95%E4%B8%89%E5%8F%89%E7%A5%9E%E7%BB%8F%E7%97%9B%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%AA%81%E5%8F%91%E7%AA%81%E6%AD%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%89%99%E7%97%9B%E8%AD%A6%E6%83%95%E4%B8%89%E5%8F%89%E7%A5%9E%E7%BB%8F%E7%97%9B%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#突发突止的牙痛警惕三叉神经痛#</span></a>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E7%89%99%E7%97%9B%E6%BA%90%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%89%E5%8F%89%E7%A5%9E%E7%BB%8F%E7%97%9B%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E7%89%99%E7%97%9B%E6%BA%90%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%89%E5%8F%89%E7%A5%9E%E7%BB%8F%E7%97%9B%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#有一种牙痛源自三叉神经痛#</span></a> 专家提醒，牙痛未必是牙病，可能神经在找茬！专家介绍，三叉神经分为三支，其中第三支为下颌支，下牙槽神经是它的一些分支。当这些神经受到干扰或者受到病理因素影响，就会引起牙齿部位的疼痛。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%8B%94%E5%AE%8C%E7%89%99%E5%90%8E%E5%8D%83%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%B8%85%E7%90%86%E7%89%99%E7%BC%9D%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%8B%94%E5%AE%8C%E7%89%99%E5%90%8E%E5%8D%83%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%B8%85%E7%90%86%E7%89%99%E7%BC%9D%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#拔完牙后千万不要清理牙缝#</span></a> <a href="http://t.cn/A6NqUL6U" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
            <pubDate>Thu, 13 Apr 2023 09:08:26 GMT</pubDate>
