            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%BF%E9%85%B8%E5%81%8F%E9%AB%98%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%93%E6%82%A3%E5%B8%95%E9%87%91%E6%A3%AE%E7%97%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%BF%E9%85%B8%E5%81%8F%E9%AB%98%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%93%E6%82%A3%E5%B8%95%E9%87%91%E6%A3%AE%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#尿酸偏高的人不易患帕金森病#</span></a>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%BF%E9%85%B8%E5%92%8C%E5%B8%95%E9%87%91%E6%A3%AE%E7%97%85%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%BF%E9%85%B8%E5%92%8C%E5%B8%95%E9%87%91%E6%A3%AE%E7%97%85%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#尿酸和帕金森病有什么关系#</span></a> 专家表示，有研究发现尿酸高的人确实不容易患帕金森病。但专家提醒，高尿酸对于帕金森病的预防作用不明确。尿酸高会引起痛风，不要为了预防帕金森病而去提高尿酸。 <a href="http://t.cn/A6NGMAQv" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a> ]]></description>
